---
---

<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Precios</div>
    <h2>Empieza gratis, crece cuando estés listo</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Sin tarjeta de crédito para empezar. Cancela cuando quieras.
    </p>

    <div class="pricing-grid">

      <div class="plan-card">
        <div class="plan-header">
          <div class="plan-name">Free</div>
          <div class="plan-price">
            <span class="price-amount">$0</span>
            <span class="price-period">/ mes</span>
          </div>
          <p class="plan-desc">Para probar y validar que SubliFlow funciona para ti.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li><span class="feat-check">✓</span> Hasta 3 equipos</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check">✓</span> Hasta 20 jugadores por equipo</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check">✓</span> 1 cliente / costurera</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check">✓</span> Exportaciones ilimitadas</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check">✓</span> Acceso desde cualquier dispositivo</li>
          <li class="feat-disabled"><span>—</span> Backups en la nube</li>
          <li class="feat-disabled"><span>—</span> Soporte prioritario</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#early-access" class="btn btn-outline plan-btn">Empieza gratis</a>
      </div>

      <div class="plan-card featured">
        <div class="plan-badge">Más popular</div>
        <div class="plan-header">
          <div class="plan-name">Pro</div>
          <div class="plan-price">
            <span class="price-amount">$19</span>
            <span class="price-period">/ mes</span>
          </div>
          <p class="plan-desc">Para talleres que producen equipos constantemente.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li><span class="feat-check accent">✓</span> Equipos ilimitados</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check accent">✓</span> Jugadores ilimitados</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check accent">✓</span> Clientes / costureras ilimitadas</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check accent">✓</span> Exportaciones ilimitadas</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check accent">✓</span> Acceso desde cualquier dispositivo</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check accent">✓</span> Backups en la nube</li>
          <li><span class="feat-check accent">✓</span> Soporte prioritario</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#early-access" class="btn btn-primary plan-btn">Empieza Pro gratis 14 días</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <p class="pricing-note">
      ¿Necesitas algo diferente? <a href="mailto:hola@subliflow.com">Contáctanos</a> para planes de equipo o volumen.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .plan-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 36px;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .plan-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--color-primary), 0 20px 40px rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .plan-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -13px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .plan-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .plan-price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .price-amount {
    font-size: 44px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .price-period {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .plan-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .plan-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .plan-features li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .feat-check {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feat-check.accent {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .feat-disabled {
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
  }

  .plan-btn {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .pricing-note {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .pricing-note a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
